{
  "texts": [
    "Mistral 8x7B, designed with the capacity to engage with multiple forms of input, stands at the forefront of this shift.",
    "Its structure, which integrates expertise across different domains, offers a template for how future models might more effectively process and synthesize information from diverse sources.",
    "The importance to enhance the multimodal capabilities of LLMs like Mistral LLM is further required by the evolving nature of online content, which is increasingly dynamic, interactive, and multimodal.",
    "The traditional text-centric view of knowledge and communication is expanding to include visual, auditory, and even tactile dimensions, reflecting the multifaceted way humans experience and interpret the world.",
    "As such, the development of AI systems capable of understanding and generating such rich, multimodal content is not just an academic pursuit but a necessary evolution to meet the demands of modern digital communication and information sharing.In this context, this article aims to explore and propose a novel method for enhancing the multimodal capabilities of Mistral 8x7B."
  ]
}